#

Pork Tenderloin with Apples

45 min
$15.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

DinnerEasyHealthy

Description

A succulent pork tenderloin roasted with sweet apples and a hint of cinnamon for a comforting, flavorful dish.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 lb
  • apples: 2 (sliced)
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • honey: 2 tbsp
  • garlic: 2 cloves (minced)
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cinnamon: 1 tsp
